body:
I've been on the forums and everyone has been ranting and just generally being unhappy. This thread is to combat that, any positive things you wanna say, say it! It could be a happy thing that happened, or a fantastic story or joke! Either way, pop some happy, intriguing and comical stuff down-lets make the  forums happy! ^-^

Also try to stay on topic, and although sometimes you need to get your few out-dont encourage flame wars

(here's one to start- who ever is reading this, have  nice day/afternoon/night!)
